On April 1, 2017, Federal State and Local Governments underwent a reorganization and employees from the Compliance Program Management unit were transplanted to Compliance, Planning & Classiﬁcation, Issue Identiﬁcation and Special Review. In addition, Compliance, Planning & Classiﬁcation assumed ownership of this manual.

New IRM 4.70.7, TE/GE Examinations, Special Review (SR) and Tax Exempt Quality Measurement System (TEQMS) Procedures, supersedes this manual, rendering this manual obsolete. Please see the new manual for all directions concerning special review for federal, state and local governments.
